@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 使用说明
# 1. 每次完整测试前，先在 Navicat 17 清库
# 2. 这个文件负责创建基础业务样例，包括 franchise / subject / record
# 3. 当前已按“一作品一记录”规则整理

### ========== franchise 样例 ==========

### F1. 系列：进击的巨人
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/franchises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Attack on Titan",
  "nameCn": "进击的巨人",
  "description": "样例系列：用于承接进击的巨人多季与 Part 结构",
  "status": "NORMAL"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("franchise_aot_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### F2. 系列：蓝色监狱
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/franchises
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Blue Lock",
  "nameCn": "蓝色监狱",
  "description": "样例系列：用于承接蓝色监狱相关作品",
  "status": "NORMAL"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("franchise_bluelock_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### ========== subject 样例 ==========

### 1. 进击的巨人 The Final Season Part 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subjects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titleCn": "进击的巨人",
  "subtitle": "The Final Season Part 1",
  "displayTitle": "进击的巨人 The Final Season Part 1",
  "seasonIndex": 4,
  "partIndex": 1,
  "franchiseId": {{franchise_aot_id}},
  "coverUrl": "https://example.com/aot-final-part1.jpg",
  "summary": "样例：巨人最终季前半部分",
  "releaseYear": 2020,
  "releaseQuarter": 4,
  "category": "ANIME",
  "studioName": "MAPPA",
  "platformLink": "https://bgm.tv/subject/aot-final-part1",
  "status": "NORMAL"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("subject_aot_p1_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 2. 进击的巨人 The Final Season Part 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/subjects
