### ========== 记录样例（一作品一记录） ==========

### A. 2024 Q1，WATCHED，48
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjectId": {{subject_aot_p1_id}},
  "recordStatus": "WATCHED",
  "scoreValue": 48,
  "recordYear": 2024,
  "recordQuarter": 1,
  "note": "样例记录A"
}
> {%
    client.global.set("record_a_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### B. 2024 Q1，WATCHED，45
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/records
Content-Type: application/json

{
